{"search_data": "Himachal PradeshHP Mukhyamantri Alpsankhyak Kalyan Yojana \u2013 Rs. 25000 for Marriage of Muslim GirlsHP Mukhyamantri Alpsankhyak Kalyan Yojana 2018The important features and highlights of this HP CM Minority Welfare Scheme are as follows:-Marriage Grant to Muslim Girls (Rs. 25,000) \u2013 The state govt. is going to provide Rs. 25000 as marriage assistance for the girls belonging to the poor Muslim families.Medical Treatment to Poor Muslim Families (Rs. 5,000) \u2013 HP govt. will provide financial assistance of Rs. 5000 for medical treatment of any poor Muslim family.Social Security Pension to Old, Widow and Disabled Muslims (Rs. 400 p.m) \u2013 The state govt. will provide Rs. 400 per month as social security pension to old, widow and disabled people from Muslim community.Minority people plays an important role in the overall development of the society. All the financial assistance would be provided to the beneficiaries through the Waqf Board.Age Limit For Social Security Pension ReducedPreviously, the state govt. has also reduce the age limit to avail social security scheme benefits. The cabinet committee has decided that the age limit for Social Security Pension is now 70 years (previously 80 years). This decision has benefited around 1.3 lakh Old Age citizens.The state govt. is going to provide necessary facilities for Muslim Graveyard \u2013 Kabristan. HP govt. will allocate land to the Waqf Board to build new burial places where Muslims can be buried after their deaths. For this purpose, deputy commissioners have been asked to find adequate spaces. Some other important announcements were also made during the launch event of Mukhyamantri Alpsankhyak Kalyan Yojana in Himachal Pradesh.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now  at  "}